A focus on long term capital growth
Our investment strategy








Riverstone Energy Limited (REL) is a closed-ended investment company listed on the London Stock Exchange under the symbol RSE, which invests exclusively in the global energy industry, with a particular focus on the exploration and production and midstream sectors.



