Strategy




About








                        Strategy
                    



                        Riverstone Holdings LLC
                    




The objective of Riverstone International Limited (the “Investment Manager”) is to achieve superior risk adjusted returns for REL through investing primarily in the exploration and production, credit and midstream energy sectors. The energy sector is global and a significant component of virtually all major economies. Long-term market drivers of economic expansion, population growth, development of markets, deregulation and privatisation will continue to create opportunities globally for investors in energy.





 











